reviewText: This DVD is so awesome!! This a rare jewel and had not to be passed on. If you are a harcore core fan of CM Punk this is for you! I couldn't be more satisfied.

This was purchased as a gift for my grandson who's into wrestling and gives me a list every year of all the tapes he wants.  He's very specific with his choices and this was one for this year.  I know he loves it.
